Class AddressInfo

java.lang.Object
  forFP1.AddressInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AddressInfo>
public class AddressInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AddressInfo>

An AddressInfo class has an Address object consisting of a static address comparator, name, and address. The address comparator is of a Comparator object. The name is of a Name object. The address is of a Address object.
